{"word":"G2145 - εὐπρόσεδρος - euprósedros - yoo-pros'-ed-ros - Attend upon","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐπρόσεδρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">euprósedros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-pros'-ed-ros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Attend upon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பற்றிக்கொண்டிருக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"sitting well towards, assiduous"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and the same as <a href=\"#/G4332 - προσεδρεύω - prosedreúō - pros-ed-ryoo'-o/4332\">G4332</a>; <i>sitting well towards</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>assiduous</i> (neuter <i>diligent service</i>): - X attend upon.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}